                    <ab>(C.) In nomine sanctae et individuae trinitatis. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/261">Cunrado</persName> divina favente
                        clementia <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Dignum est, ut
                        qui prudenter dei obsequia ordinare procurant et hoc ad stabilitatem
                        perpetuam nostram corroborationem confirmare exposcunt, ut tanto libentius
                        obaudiant, quanto deo placita intellegimus et prudentia, deo protegente bono
                        studio ad effectum perducere procuravimus. Igitur omnium fidelium sanctae
                        dei aecclesiae ac nostrorum presentium scilicet et futurorum comperiat
                        sollertia, quia, dum nos dilecto fideli nostro <persName key="#Abbots"><name
                                ref="Winizo">Uuinizoni</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">cenobium</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/301"
                            key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Castle #Clusae/gates #Roads #Plebs #Decima #Public_exactions #Angaria #Churches #Monasteries #Cells/hermitages #Abbots #Monks"
                            >domini et Salvatoris in <placeName ref="#places/737">monte
                                Amiate</placeName></orgName> constitutum ad regendum commisissemus,
                        et ibidem neglecta dei obsequia et procurationem deo ibidem famulantium
                        predecessorum suorum incuriam multis modis repperisse, studiosius decertavit
                        congregationem <rs key="#Monks">monachorum</rs> ibidem deo servientium
                        regulariter corrigere et solummodo divinis obsequiis deditos ad
                        sufficientiam suorum largire, quatenus prelatus iam fati monasterii domini
                        Salvatoris qui per tempora fuerit ac successorum illius abbatis vel
                        prepositi cum subiectis monachis suorum inibi deo servientium deinceps in
                        futurum sufficienter habere mereantur, ob amorem dei remediumque anime
                        nostrae ac successorum nostrorum regum aut imperatorum conferens eis ad
                        sufficientiam suorum <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">cellam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >sancti Benedicti in Bucino</orgName>, <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Plebs">plebem</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Plebs"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/302">sanctae Mariae in Lamule</orgName>, <rs
                            key="#Curtes">curtem</rs>
                        <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><orgName ref="#juridical_persons/303">sancti Stephani</orgName> in
                                <placeName ref="#places/757">Monticclo</placeName></geogName> cum
                            <rs key="#Castle">castro Monti latronis</rs>, <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curtem</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/331">Mustia</geogName> cum <rs key="#Castle">castro Monte
                            nigro</rs>, <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2335">Luminiana</geogName> cum <rs key="#Curtes">castro
                            Monte Pinzutulo</rs>, sicut <persName><name ref="Hubertus"
                                >Ubertus</name></persName>
                        <rs>ad manum suam detinuit</rs>, <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs>
                        <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2336">sancti Miniati</geogName>, <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curtem</rs>
                        <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >sancti Quirici</geogName> in <placeName>Piscinule</placeName> et
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2310">sancti Simeonis</geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2337">sancti Peregrini</geogName> et <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curtem</rs>
                        <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2309">sanctae Mariae de Offena</geogName> cum <rs>roccae
                            quae nominantur Saxine</rs>, <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/334">Palea</geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2313">sancti Sebastiani</geogName>, curtem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2338">sancti Stephani</geogName> in <placeName
                            ref="#places/2748">Tutona</placeName>, curtem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/335">sancti Clementis in Titinano</geogName> cum Cerris et
                            <rs key="#Angaria">angariales</rs>, curtem de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2339">Mussona</geogName> cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terra de Redola maiore et minore et Bitena et Canneta et
                        Herminula</rs>, medietatem de curte <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            ref="#estates/2340">sancti Lazari</geogName> cum sua <rs key="#Churches"
                            >aecclesia</rs>, curtem de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2315">Feroniano</geogName>, curtem de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2341">Citiliano</geogName> et curtem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2342">sancti Salvatoris</geogName> in
                            <placeName>Uigugnano</placeName>, curtem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2334">sancti Seueri</geogName> super <rs key="#Lakes"
                            >lacum</rs> et curticella de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/333">Bisenzo</geogName>, curtem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2343">sancti Iohannis</geogName> in
                            <placeName>Uariano</placeName> et <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2344">sancti Saturnini</geogName>, curtem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2345">sancti Columbani</geogName> et curtem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><orgName ref="#juridical_persons/308">sancti Salvatoris in valle
                                Racana</orgName></geogName>, cellam sanctae <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >Mariae in Ualeriano</orgName>, curticella in <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Wine #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2346">Curticiule</geogName> cum <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> et <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs>, quae
                        est prope <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio Uarano</rs>, curtem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2317">sancti Salvatoris in Campagnatico</geogName>, curtem
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2311">sancti Petri in Ceruaria</geogName> et curtem
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >sancti Stephani in Iuniano</geogName>, curtem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >sanctae Seuere in Paterno</geogName> cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >campo Albiniano</rs>, curticella quae nominatur <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Crostule</geogName> et curticella in <placeName key="#Curtes"
                            >Cursinianu</placeName> cum omnibus pertinentiis et adiacentiis suis,
                        cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >sancti Petri in Latera</orgName> et cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >sancti Petri in Garmarita cum sancto Anastasio</orgName>, cellam
                            <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >sancti Sauini</orgName> et cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >sanctae Restite</orgName> et <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >sancti Petri</orgName> et <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >sancti Stephani in Tarquini</orgName>, cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >sanctae Marie in Corgnitu</orgName> per locas designatas: de una parte
                        ripa cum petra quae divisa est a ripa, de alia parte <rs key="#Walls"
                            >muro</rs> quae claudit ipsum <rs key="#Castle">castellum</rs>, de alia
                        parte <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs> quae venit per <rs
                            key="#Clusae/gates">portam</rs> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra
                                    <persName><name ref="Azo">Azonis</name></persName></rs> filii
                                <persName><name ref="Berizus">Berizi</name></persName> cum suis
                        consortibus, de quarta vero parte est <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra
                            filii <persName><name ref="Allo">Alonis</name></persName></rs> -- et
                        sunt <rs key="#Size">pedes duo centum per longum, similiter per latum</rs>
                        --, ea videlicet ratione ut ad ab hac in futurum predicta sancta congregatio
                        his omnibus denominatis cellulis et curtibus cum suis omnibus pertinentiis
                        et adiacentiis tantummodo suis utilitatibus habentes victum vestitumque
                        regulariter summentes absque ulla dilatione solummodo divinis die noctuque
                        persistant obsequiis ac pro stabilitate totius imperii nobis a deo commissi
                        studeant exorare. Sed quod bono studio bonaque voluntate feci, perhennem
                        habeat stabilitatem, petiit pietatem nostram, ut eandem ordinationem nostra
                        confirmaremus conscriptionem, sicuti et fecimus. Denique etiam concedimus
                        predicto monasterio omnes <rs key="#Decima">decimas</rs> frea et iudiciaria
                        vel omne[m] compositionem et <rs key="#Public_exactions">exhibitionem</rs>
                        publicam ex omnibus manentibus de supra memoratis cellulis et curtibus ob
                        remedium animae nostrae successorumque nostrorum regum vel imperatorum qui
                        per tempora fuerint ad portam ipsius monasterii conferendam semper ad usus
                        peregrinorum sustentandos in alimoniam et augmentum animae nostre propter
                        oppressiones malorum ac pravorum hominum, quae sufferre minime nec
                        sustentare potuerant. Quapropter eidem sancto loco hoc nostrum preceptum
                        fieri iussimus, per quod precipimus, ut ab hac in futurum eadem sancta
                        congregatio cum omni quietudine absque ullo publico repetitu ac rectoris
                        loci ipsius subtractu easdem cellulas et curtes in suis utilitatibus ac
                        necessitatibus habeant et ordinent, faciant et disponant, quatenus exinde
                        sufficientiam habentes in divinis obsequiis et nobis eorum famulatio
                        proficiant sempiternale remedium. Si qui vero, quod futurum minime credimus
                        esse, quilibet homo magna parvaque persona contra hoc nostrum imperiale
                        muniminis preceptum temerario ausu contendere aut inrumpere, molestare aut
                        inquietare seu et vacuare vel diminorare aut etiam inbeficiare predictas
                        cellulas atque ipsum supra dictum monasterium atque curtes presumpserit aut
                        aliqua violentiam quandoque inferre presumptor extiterit, sciat se
                        compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras centum</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Camera_regis">medietatem kamere nostre</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem eisdem aecclesiae
                            rectoribus</rs>. Et ut haec nostre auctoritatis preceptum futuris
                        temporibus domino opitulante valeat inconvulsum manere, manu propria subter
                        firmavimus et anuli nostri impressione subter insigniri iussimus. Signum
                        domni Cvnradi (M.) invictissimi imperatoris augusti. <persName
                            key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Hugo">Hugo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> vice domni <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Archbishops"><name ref="Aribo"
                            >Ariboni</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Archbishops">archiepiscopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> cognovit. Data anno dominicae incarnationis
                        MXXVII, regni vero domni Chuonradi secundi regnantis III, imperii eius
                        primo, indicione X; acta in <placeName ref="#places/52">civitate
                            Leoniana</placeName> non. April.</ab>
                </div>
